<March 1518.)

[An autograph rough draft, on the back of the rough draft of Ep. 801 3 which was written by Bruno for Froben. The two letters are evidently contemporary, and the contents indicate beyond doubt that this is addressed to Erasmus. Many of the sentences are written more than once, in varying forms which need not be preserved in full ; but, where desirable, I have used αι and ει2 to denote earlier and later alternatives.]
